POST / HTTP /<HTTP Version>
For HTTP protocol version that recommended to HTTP 1.1 only.
Authorization: Basic <Base 64 Encoding>
This parameter use for request access to SMSGW by user/password that encryption by Base64 encoding.
Content-Type:<Content type>
The type of HTTP content that recommended to use “text/xml” only
Charset: <character encoding>

For specify the character encoding of the HTTP content relate to content type. You can use UTF-8 or TIS-620
If not set the web server shall be use default encoding to decode the HTTP content instead.
Content-Length:<length of HTTP content>
For specify the number of charactors in HTTP content.
Connection:<type of connection>
The type of connection that connect to SMSGW it have 2 mode.
Connection:Close: Single requests to use a single connection.
Connection:Keep-Alive: Multiple requests to use a single connection (Recommended).

Host:<Server IP address>:<TCP port>
For specify destination IP address and port of SMSGW


